WEBVTT

00:00.115 --> 00:02.182
Previously on "Heartland":

00:02.250 --> 00:03.750
What are you doing here?

00:03.817 --> 00:06.186
How come you're not picking up
or returning my calls?

00:06.254 --> 00:07.387
Don't you think the guest room

00:07.455 --> 00:09.189
would make the perfect nursery?

00:09.257 --> 00:11.024
Well, no, actually, I don't.

00:11.959 --> 00:13.360
Caleb odell,

00:13.428 --> 00:16.763
would you be
my lawfully wedded husband?

00:16.830 --> 00:18.297
I will.

00:18.365 --> 00:21.534
One game, you and me.
Five thousand bus.S.

00:23.970 --> 00:25.104
Yes!

00:25.172 --> 00:27.139
Shut up and take the money,
all right?

00:27.207 --> 00:28.240
We're partners.

00:28.308 --> 00:29.741
Pay off some of that debt.

00:29.809 --> 00:30.943
Thanks, man.

00:31.945 --> 00:34.512
Well, you know
how I feel about the...

00:34.580 --> 00:36.347
T n nursery.

00:36.415 --> 00:38.149
Well, I figured
you'd keep on me

00:38.217 --> 00:40.085
until you got
what you wanted anyway, so.

00:40.152 --> 00:41.386
Oh, thank you!

00:42.988 --> 00:43.988
Careful!

00:44.056 --> 00:45.390
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!

00:45.458 --> 00:46.624
Okay.

00:46.692 --> 00:47.992
W-watch the door there.

00:48.060 --> 00:50.127
Now, Caleb,
lower on the left side there.

00:50.195 --> 00:51.562
Whose left, Lou?

00:51.629 --> 00:52.629
Okay, watch the door frame,
grandpa!

00:52.697 --> 00:54.064
You're gonna scratch the wood.

00:54.132 --> 00:55.932
Now, both of you could
twist it a little bit.

00:56.000 --> 00:56.967
A little more...

00:57.034 --> 00:58.502
Lou, please!

00:58.570 --> 01:01.105
This whole exercise is crazy.

01:01.172 --> 01:03.107
I don't know why I let myself
get talked into it!

01:03.174 --> 01:05.141
Okay, just careful
on the stairs there.

01:05.209 --> 01:07.110
Excuse me, Lou.
Sorry.

01:07.177 --> 01:08.511
Where are you going?
I thought you were gonna help!

01:08.579 --> 01:10.213
I've got stuff to do.

01:10.280 --> 01:12.014
So "stuff" is more important
than your role

01:12.082 --> 01:13.549
as a future aunt?

01:15.519 --> 01:16.719
- Hey, mom!
- Hey, sweetheart!

01:16.786 --> 01:18.254
I'm so glad you're here.

01:18.322 --> 01:19.355
I've gotta run over
some wedding details with you.

01:19.423 --> 01:21.023
I'm actually just on my way out.

01:21.091 --> 01:23.024
Well, honey,
I've gotta talk to you

01:23.092 --> 01:24.192
because it's countdown time.

01:24.260 --> 01:25.793
It's only a month away!

01:25.861 --> 01:27.195
The polo club needs
dinner numbers,

01:27.263 --> 01:28.997
so we have got to finalize
the guest list.

01:29.064 --> 01:31.233
I'm sorry, I can't right now.

01:32.701 --> 01:34.669
Ashley, have you at least
picked your bridesmaids?

01:34.737 --> 01:36.204
Look.

01:36.272 --> 01:37.838
I'm really happy that
you're helping me with this,

01:37.905 --> 01:40.274
but I already told you
no bridesmaids,

01:40.342 --> 01:41.675
and Caleb doesn't want
a best man.

01:41.743 --> 01:42.676
Oh...

01:42.744 --> 01:44.578
Okay?
So don't worry!

01:44.646 --> 01:45.812
I love you!

01:45.880 --> 01:46.947
Yeah.

01:48.550 --> 01:49.883
Hey, val.

01:51.052 --> 01:52.719
Honest to God...

01:54.688 --> 01:56.789
Sometimes I think this wedding
isn't worth the time,

01:56.857 --> 01:58.291
the money, or the effort!

02:02.729 --> 02:05.331
How are you?
How's school going?

02:05.399 --> 02:06.866
It's going.

02:08.935 --> 02:11.002
What're you doing
with that rock?

02:12.138 --> 02:13.905
I'm building a fire pit.

02:13.973 --> 02:16.375
It's gonna be awesome!

02:17.710 --> 02:19.511
Lou, would you like some help?

02:19.579 --> 02:21.880
I am pregnant, not broken.

02:21.947 --> 02:22.881
Ungh!

02:22.948 --> 02:24.316
Okay, it's too heavy.

02:24.384 --> 02:27.151
God, what's in that box, lead?

02:29.555 --> 02:32.089
Grandpa,
don't make that face.

02:32.157 --> 02:33.457
Come on.

02:33.525 --> 02:35.159
We agreed
this was a good idea.

02:35.227 --> 02:37.195
Whoa! Look at this!

02:39.498 --> 02:42.232
Best all around cowboy,
ponoka stampede!

02:42.333 --> 02:43.633
Okay, Caleb, come on.

02:43.701 --> 02:44.801
Drool over it
on the front lawn.

02:44.868 --> 02:45.802
Let's go.

02:45.869 --> 02:46.936
Yes, ma'am.

